title: udemy.com - Photo Gallery with PHP, MySQL, ImageMagick and jQuer
description:
Year : 2013
Video Format : MP4 
Video : MPEG4 Video (H264) 800x600 8fps 303kbps 
Audio : AAC 44100Hz mono 45kbps 


This course explains how to create a simple photo gallery, where administrator can upload, resize and crop the image to the relevant dimensions.

Cropping and resizing is made using ImageMagick.

The front end of the gallery will display all uploaded images, grouped under number of categories and images will reveal the larger / full size image using jQuery lightbox.
